Case Notes
  Failure of architect to renew registration does not warrant forfeiture of the benefits of the architect's contracts if forfeiture would be wholly out of proportion to requirements of public policy or appropriate punishment.  57 H. 124, 551 P.2d 525.
  Provision for renewal not for public protection but for revenue.  57 H. 124, 551 P.2d 525.
